"Waterloo University. We are informed that the CS club at Waterloo formerly "
"had a sign on its door reading \"Ye Olde Foo Bar and Grill\"; this led to an"
" attempt to establish \"grill\" as the third metasyntactic variable, but it "
"never caught on."
